{"word":"Abraham","slug":"abraham","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abraham</b> <a href=\"#/H85\">H85</a> <br/> Called also Abram.<br/> Son of Terah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=27'>Gen 11:27</a><br/> Marries Sarah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=29'>Gen 11:29</a><br/> Dwells in Ur, but removes to Haran<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=31'>Gen 11:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=7'>Neh 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=4'>Act 7:4</a><br/> Dwells in Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=6'>Gen 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=4'>Act 7:4</a><br/> Divine call of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=3'>Gen 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=3'>Jos 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=7'>Neh 9:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=51&verse=2'>Isa 51:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=3'>Act 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=8'>Heb 11:8</a><br/> Canaan given to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=1'>Gen 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=7'>Gen 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=21'>Gen 15:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=24'>Eze 33:24</a><br/> Dwells in Beth-El<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=8'>Gen 12:8</a><br/> Sojourns in Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=20'>Gen 12:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in