ases a place for her burial, and buries her in a cave<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=20'>Gen 23:20</a><br/> Marries Keturah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=1'>Gen 25:1</a><br/> Provides a wife for Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24'>Gen 24</a><br/> Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=15'>Gen 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=3'>Gen 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=4'>Gen 25:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=34'>1Ch 1:34</a><br/> Testament of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=6'>Gen 25:6</a><br/> Wealth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=13&verse=2'>Gen 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=24&verse=35'>Gen 24:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=51&verse=2'>Isa 51:2</a><br/> Age of, at different periods<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=12&verse=4'>Gen 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=16'>Gen 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=5'>Gen 21:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=7'>Gen 25:7</a><br/> Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=15'>Gen 15:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=10'>Gen 25:10</a><br/> In Paradise<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=11'>Mat 8:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=28'>Luk 13:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=16&verse=31'>Luk 16:31</a><br/> Friend of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2